CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 18, 1959, pg. A12 reads: "Baby Shower - Mrs. Audrey Johnson gave a baby shower for her niece, Mrs. Delores Woodford, recently, and the following were guests and brought lovely gifts. Left to right, standing: Jean Bruce, Lucille Howell, Helen Floyd, Carol Strother and Edna Jones.  Mrs. Johnson and Mrs. Woodford are seated. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of seven women, back row from left: Jean Bruce, Lucille Howell, Helen Floyd, Carol Strother and Edna Jones; seated: Audrey Johnson, and Delores Woodford, guest of honor, gathered on porch for baby shower
